====== Concat Table Plugin for DokuWiki ======

 * Gets tables from other pages, combines them and outputs the result
 * Can also be used to include and reformat a single table

Usage:
  {{concattable>page1#section|page2#section}}
  {{concattable>page1#section|page2#section&flags}}
	
Available Flags:
  rows			formats the table with rows
  cols			formats the table with columns
  noheadings	removes all table headings from the entire table

Further documentation is coming.


